{"tid":1652844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該，大家應該要覺醒！","createTime":"2019-10-13T23:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T23:38:04.000Z","uid":318148,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"55522c4623881fb08fd271b2c8e56be7b08d62b9","tid":1652844,"uid":318148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T23:28:05.000Z","msg":"係武力咁不平等既情況，仲要用力敵依個方法去對抗政權，對我地真係太唔公平。<br />\n<br />\n你話掟磚同火魔法，其實班狗之前都已經示範咗點解決，就係用裝甲車衝，所有磚同魔法都收皮，連rb都冇撚用。<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無限期三罷，再落街打遊擊戰，目標針對係中銀，交行，建行，小米等所有中資企業；另一方面，叫民陣隔一兩星期發起一次大遊行，壯聲勢，聚民心，咁先係最有效方法</span>"},{"pid":"295b54b38ad57cdbb241edba34c5b36c3fe3925f","tid":1652844,"uid":318148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T23:29:18.000Z","msg":"外國人點解會肯用火魔法，就係因為人哋嗰個係民主嘅政府，佢哋知個政府到最後會跪低。但我哋對呢個政府係極權政府，佢係唔會跪低㗎。所以我哋先至要轉玩法，唔好同佢硬碰硬。到最後只會係我哋蝕底"},{"pid":"62bc10681fbf1a27f42da5f3cd666f15c5fb4a5a","tid":1652844,"uid":318148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T23:30:46.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"f15b3af42eb9aeb456bf5c5f859a3743929b5a68","tid":1652844,"uid":318148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T23:31:11.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"c33cd2310be13c3b7bd313f5a54b43b27b8033c6","tid":1652844,"uid":318148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T23:31:51.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d661c8eed1b21c242d61129ab5ac296996d018e","tid":1652844,"uid":318148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T23:32:26.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"b05b4990f040caf259f356b8c7f1e799310a0e14","tid":1652844,"uid":318148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T23:33:24.000Z","msg":"唔想再見到咁多手足俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/